Personal Loans Online - Est. in 1962 | World Finance















































Skip to content



  Menu




About World Finance Corporation


Meeting the Needs of Our
Customers Since 1962. 
Personalized Service
For the past 50 years, World Finance has been helping people realize their financial goals by offering fixed rate and payment loan solutions. With branches nationwide, we are part of the communities in which we serve. Our branches are staffed with friendly, knowledgeable Associates who live and work right in your town. They understand your needs and are available to meet with you one-on-one to discuss your loan options. 
 Nationwide Locations
When you need to borrow money, World Finance is here as a financial neighbor you can rely on and trust. Since 1962, we’ve been committed to helping our neighbors thrive and grow by supporting their financial needs. With us, you get the strength of a national financial institution and the personal services of local neighborhood branches. It’s one of the top reasons millions of customers choose us.
 






Over the past 50 years, from our humble beginnings to now, the World Finance emphasis has always been quality customer service and a drive to build strong personal relationships with customers. Many of our loans today are from existing customers who like our hassle-free process and personal service. 

 





Because we have locations in 15 states, it's easy to connect with our caring Associates right in your community, convenient to where you work and live.
Find the World Finance branch location that's most convenient for you. 
Facts at a Glance:

Opened in 1962
Nearly 1,200 branches
Over 3,500 Associates in 15 states
Serving over one million customers per year

 We’re Committed to Your Community
We don’t just work in your community. We live here, too. That’s why we get involved in a variety of local programs and organizations to help build stronger communities. Our Associates are active volunteers with local and national charities and we’re regular sponsors of local events that bring neighbors together.
 




We're a Trusted Partner You Can Count On. Our  Associates are committed to working with you to find the solution that fits your situation and your budget. They’re knowledgeable about the products and services World Finance offers and are ready to help you make the best loan decision.
 
Apply for a Personal Loan Just Got Easier!
Your branch service Associate will work with you one-on-one and answer questions you have about our loans, payment options, and what’s needed to apply. If you need help while completing your application, just call or stop by your local World Finance branch and our Associates will assist you. We’re with you every step of the way to make our loan process simple, fast and the right fit for you.
 We’re in Your Neighborhood
With local branches in 15 states, it’s simple to find a World Finance location in your community. Whether you want a personal loan for an auto repair, to make a home repair or for other common personal loan reasons, we’re here to help you find the loan that fits your personal situation.
 We’re Here to Answer Your Questions
If you’d like to know more about World Finance, the documents and information you need to qualify for one of our easy loans, or how to complete your loan application, call or stop by your local branch and talk to one of our awesome Associates.
 





Though we operate under several names, all of our subsidiaries offer the same quality service.
  

World Acceptance Corporation is a publicly traded company on NASDAQ under the symbol WRLD.
Subsidiaries – World Acceptance Corporation offers our loan product services in Alabama, Georgia, Idaho, Illinois, Indiana, Kentucky, Louisiana, Missouri, Mississippi, New Mexico, Oklahoma, South Carolina, Tennessee, Texas and Wisconsin. All of our branches are fully licensed in and supervised by each state’s regulatory agency. All loans are subject to our credit underwriting standards.
State Resources – download SC Consumer Rights & Responsibilities PDF





















